      "content": "that's a good start. i want to make sure the essay doesn't sound like it's just ignoring the other side, but i want the counter-arguments to look weak. can you add a section where i address the 'meritocracy' argument? i want to show how that idea is basically just an excuse to keep the status quo going. how should i phrase that so it sounds like a logical critique?",
